"### Deep Sky-Objekte\n"
"\n"
"Some deep space objects were also discovered in ancient China, which were "
"also included in the Xingguans.\n"
"\n"
"Beziehe folgendes ein:\n"
"\n"
"|Allgemeiner Name|Chinesischer Name|Pinyin|Übersetzung|Spitzname|\n"
